parameters:
Bunny-chan: Alright, tonight's Monster Fight has begun!!
Today we have an incredible battle between big names♪

Spectator: Bunny-chan, I love you!! Today's the day I'll win
big on my bet and make a fortune~!!

Spectator: With this match, two of the city's four major
organizations will merge! The power map of the underworld is
going to be redrawn~!! It's a historic battle!

Anomalocaris Mosman: Mosmos~! So you've come toddling in to
be my stepping stone! Once it's over, you'll become one of
my underlings... Don't put up a pathetic fight, got it?

Memimi: That's my line! Naturally, you'll become the lowest
rank in our organization... But don't be discouraged, start
from scratch and do your best!

Anomalocaris Mosman: Still running your mouth...
Unfortunately for you, when you become the lowest rank in my
organization, I plan to bully you thoroughly, so brace
yourself!!

Bunny-chan: Okaaay, 10 seconds to start~. Please get to your
starting positions❤︎ Good luck to both of you~❤︎
'街でアクリルキーホルダーを売ろう！飽きたらアジトに帰ってアノマロカリスモスマンに報告しよう！'

Anomalocaris Mosman: You fool... You've lost your focus!
You're wide open！！！

Bunny-chan: The victory goes to Anomalocaris Mosman-san!
Congratulations~❤︎ With this, the Ocean Predator Empire will
be integrated into the Poison Darkness Cambrian!

Anomalocaris Mosman: Momo... Mosmosmos-! With this, my
organization is now top 3 in the city! I'll take the Shark
guy's underlings, the turf's convenience stores, and the
lucrative drug trade too~!!

The Shark Duke was defeated, and his organization was
dissolved...
